        {
            "title": "《愛回家》｜滕麗名迎49歲生日 「熊家人」搞驚喜送4個蛋糕兼18個壽桃",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"《愛回家》｜滕麗名迎49歲生日 「熊家人」搞驚喜送4個蛋糕兼壽桃\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/20fa0dd5b14b6c77a4184234cb0be12e/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250110/_2025011014005725703.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">《愛回家》｜滕麗名迎49歲生日 「熊家人」搞驚喜送4個蛋糕兼壽桃</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>TVB處境劇《愛•回家之開心速遞》向來受歡迎，在劇中飾演熊尚善一角的滕麗名，更深得觀眾愛戴，滕麗名亦與劇中一班演員建立了深厚感情。滕麗名即將於1月20日迎來49歲生日，日前「熊家」上下就為壽星女提早慶祝。\n\n</p><h2>滕麗名被愛包圍</h2>\n<p>滕麗名在社交網大曬多張與「熊家」的慶生照，見他們在開工期間為壽星女送上驚喜，除準備了壽桃包，更有4個生日蛋糕，寫上滕麗名不同身份的稱呼，眾人拿著壽桃包開心合照，畫面十分有愛，滕麗名寫道：「Thanks hunt’s family #愛回家之開心速遞 #熊家人」。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4009146/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"滕麗名於1月20日迎49歲生日。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/af57bffa642c728967dc648c62ecb731/2025-01/WhatsApp_Image_2025-01-10_at_13_20_11_2_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        滕麗名於1月20日迎49歲生日。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4009147/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"「熊家人」為滕麗名慶生。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6b78534cc0596ed0e3e38fbe44a6c087/2025-01/WhatsApp_Image_2025-01-10_at_13_20_11_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        「熊家人」為滕麗名慶生。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4009148/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"滕麗名又叫SHEEPY。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/505039bf0aae23854102ff1ac807555b/2025-01/WhatsApp_Image_2025-01-10_at_13_20_11.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        滕麗名又叫SHEEPY。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4009149/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"呂慧儀向滕麗名送上祝福：「家姐生辰快樂！」\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/17e4e5f5bf595d40b62b397a556bb50c/2025-01/WhatsApp_Image_2025-01-10_at_13_20_10_2_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        呂慧儀向滕麗名送上祝福：「家姐生辰快樂！」\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4009150/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"滕麗名在社交網大曬多張與「熊家」的慶生照。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/476d485e7e5129a0ef067b114031d760/2025-01/WhatsApp_Image_2025-01-10_at_13_20_10_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        滕麗名在社交網大曬多張與「熊家」的慶生照。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4009151/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"大夥在開工期間為壽星女送上驚喜，有壽桃包和生日蛋糕。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/653a9201146d45dc67494311428d32e9/2025-01/WhatsApp_Image_2025-01-10_at_13_20_10.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        大夥在開工期間為壽星女送上驚喜，有壽桃包和生日蛋糕。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4009152/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"滕麗名拍劇時收驚喜提早慶生。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/32e4e1df9968b0f2fa5f36cf915a4941/2025-01/WhatsApp_Image_2025-01-10_at_13_20_09.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        滕麗名拍劇時收驚喜提早慶生。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>呂慧儀亦在其社交網分享多張合照，並向滕麗名送上祝福：「家姐生辰快樂！祝妳年年歡樂，歲歲平安！#農曆生日 #熊家寶寶 #有愛的熊家人 #愛妳 #有愛的11廠」。\n\n</p>\n<p>相關文章︰<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/film-drama/3347274/%E6%8B%8D%E6%AA%94%E5%BB%9A%E6%88%BF%E4%B8%A8%E9%BB%83%E7%BF%A0%E5%A6%82-%E8%95%AD%E6%AD%A3%E6%A5%A0%E5%90%8C%E5%A0%B4%E6%89%93%E6%83%85%E7%BD%B5%E4%BF%8F-%E6%96%B9%E5%8A%9B%E7%94%B3%E8%87%AA%E7%88%86%E6%84%9B%E7%94%A8%E5%BB%9A%E8%97%9D%E6%B0%B9%E5%A5%B3%E5%8F%8B-%E6%BB%95%E9%BA%97%E5%90%8D%E7%85%B2%E9%9B%9E%E6%B9%AF%E6%90%B5%E8%80%81%E5%85%AC%E5%81%9A%E7%99%BD%E8%80%81%E9%BC%A0\">拍檔廚房丨黃翠如 蕭正楠同場打情罵俏 方力申自爆愛用廚藝氹女友 滕麗名煲雞湯搵老公做白老鼠</a>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2046316/即時-娛樂-愛回家-滕麗名迎49歲生日-熊家人-搞驚喜送4個蛋糕兼18個壽桃",
